## 14. Implementation Notes

### 14.1 CSS Variables 적용 예시

```css
:root {
    /* Colors */
  --color-purple-700: #8B5CF6;
  --color-purple-600: #9F7AEA;
  --color-purple-100: #F5F3FF;
  --color-gray-900: #1F2937;
  --color-gray-100: #F9FAFB;
  --color-white: #FFFFFF;
  
  /* Spacing */
  --spacing-xs: 4px;
  --spacing-sm: 8px;
  --spacing-md: 16px;
  --spacing-lg: 24px;
  --spacing-xl: 32px;
  
  /* Typography */
  --font-primary: "Pretendard", sans-serif;
  --text-h1: 2.25rem;
  --text-body: 1rem;
  
  /* Shadows */
  --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,
    0,
    0,
    0.05);
  --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,
    0,
    0,
    0.07);
  --shadow-purple: 0 4px 12px rgba(139,
    92,
    246,
    0.15);
  
  /* Radius */
  --radius-sm: 4px;
  --radius-md: 8px;
  --radius-lg: 12px;
  
  /* Transitions */
  --transition-base: 200ms ease;
}
```

